{"tid":1331532,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[波台統計學]其實整多10條連儂隧道 維穩費已經多咗一億","createTime":"2019-07-19T03:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T03:51:43.000Z","uid":134997,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"abbe99aff69388734c1d949d2fd03129f735a79c","tid":1331532,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:26:11.000Z","msg":"外面傳聞一件$300，明眼人都知依啲job要判上判咗最少5次先會得返$300咁少，如果唔係凌晨出嚟邊撚個做，平時翻凌晨間都雙工啦，粗略估計大判二判三判都最少食咗$500，連埋交通津貼飯錢當一件$800，請400人買埋物資飯盒加埋book旅遊巴，計少啲，我當出一次show要30萬。<br />\n<br />\n但我地手足一日已經recover返，佢地夠膽keep住咁同我地玩，最好一星期出一次show，一年53個星期，已經用超過1000萬，整多10條隧道，佢地含撚都無味道。"},{"pid":"d27fdca825fa30922e2a1e3eeb3cf50de15dc9ce","tid":1331532,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:30:08.000Z","msg":"規模夠大<br />\n就要更多人清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481c8b822f59b15eb9769063d5e05bb3e5662d7f","tid":1331532,"uid":134997,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:31:24.000Z","msg":"貼八國聯軍旗：$10/1張<br />\n撕memo紙：$1/1張<br />\n貼示威者大頭相：$20/張<br />\n火燒連環牆：$2000 俾人扣查雙工，縱火坐監+$100000安家費<br />\n飯錢有得claim，有旅遊巴接送"},{"pid":"ec0bc59799e54dbad9401074e04da4c438ba67e3","tid":1331532,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d27fdca825fa30922e2a1e3eeb3cf50de15dc9ce","tid":1331532,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:30:08.000Z","msg":"規模夠大<br />\n就要更多人清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:32:21.000Z","msg":"有無手足開發大欖隧道"},{"pid":"e5f70eca8a8797c68dbd7cf4ccdee3352a2fbdbf","tid":1331532,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d27fdca825fa30922e2a1e3eeb3cf50de15dc9ce","tid":1331532,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:30:08.000Z","msg":"規模夠大<br />\n就要更多人清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:36:51.